==French==
===Etymology===
Old French [[taisir]], from Latin [[tacere]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/tɛʀ/}}

===Verb===
'''taire'''
# (''transitive'') To [[quieten]], to [[shut up]], to [[silence]]
#:''Taisez vos enfants!''
#::''Shut your children up!''

'''se taire'''
# (''intransitive'') To [[shut up]], to fall [[silent]]
#:''Tais-toi!''
#::''Shut up!''

